          <a href="https://coschedule.com/blog/creative-blog-post-ideas-and-topics" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Click here</a> to get your creative juices flowing! 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style={{ flexBasis: "30%", marginLeft: "40px" }}>
